Whether you are in town for leisure or business, find a range of interesting and convenient activities while staying at the Embassy Suites Santa Ana – Orange County Airport North hotel. Centrally located in the heart of Orange County just 2.5 miles from the John Wayne / Orange County Airport, our hotel provides an easily accessible home base while exploring some world-famous area attractions. With Disneyland just minutes away, the Embassy Suites provides an affordable Disney hotel experience with additional unique amenities. Whether you are planning a trip around an attraction or exploring town during down time, this hotel in Santa Ana, California is located near Hwy 55, Hwy 22, I-5, and I-405 which makes trips to Anaheim, Costa Mesa, Huntington Beach, Irvine, Newport Beach, and Tustin quick and easy.
